title: "Agentic Reasoning Protocol (ARP) — Open Specification"
message: "If you implement ARP or reference it in a paper, please cite the underlying whitepaper that introduces the protocol."
type: software
authors:
  - name: "Anlora"
    website: "https://meetanlora.com"
    affiliation: "Anlora (brand operating pre-incorporation)"
identifiers:
